MOTORISTS have a idea that just because you can afford to buy a powerful car, then you automatically have the skills to handle it. Footage of an E92 M3 driver trying to drift but crashing the car has surfaced on social media. In the video, the driver can be seen going towards a corner at high speeds, as the driver approaches the corner, he seemingly tries to pull a drifting manuvre but loses control of the car. The incident reportedly happened Auburn, California. 